{"tid":1678944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(呀~~ 又唔讀書) 警方查攝記身份證明文件 質疑證件有「電訊盈科」字眼","createTime":"2019-10-28T02:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:00:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0b18092b04025a086ea6404ca3dfaa699037a1","tid":1678944,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xn4LapFqOUguY1LCTSIOgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD05MzEuNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/G0D_XZEaB98xIz7Jo1iBsw--~B/aD05NjA7dz0xMjgwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-10/689a7060-f898-11e9-b3ce-819754d3635f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fxn4LapFqOUguY1LCTSIOgg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD05MzEuNQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FG0D_XZEaB98xIz7Jo1iBsw--~B%2FaD05NjA7dz0xMjgwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2F689a7060-f898-11e9-b3ce-819754d3635f&h=40588882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民發起在尖沙咀梳士巴利花園集會，主題是「連繫穆斯林、守護民眾、與記者同行」。<br />\n<br />\n集會未開始，現場已有一批市民聚集，部分人手持標語、戴上口罩，又向在場戒備的防暴警察高叫「解散警隊，刻不容緩」。多名穿著防暴裝備的警員，以圍巾遮蓋鼻及口等位置。有警員一度截查多人，被圍觀人士指罵，批評警方蒙面執法。<br />\n<br />\n在警方截查現場人士期間，有包括NOW新聞台攝影師在旁拍攝。該名攝影師遭警員詢問他的身份並要求他展示身份證及記者證，警方質疑他的員工證上為何寫有「電訊盈科」字眼。<br />\n<br />\n亦有人向在場人士派發在早前NBA比賽中聲援香港的衣服，有人則在場揮動美國國旗。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488440-20191027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488440-20191027.htm&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=031632b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488440-20191027.htm&h=94d26f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488440-20191027.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dea1aff6a5d4583fca562305ec724985573accf3","tid":1678944,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3gbRGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3gbRGC.jpg&h=94dd7b77&s={SIZE}\" />老豆搵仔：新疆單野俾譚仔搞到沉晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676450</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a91ad88c7a1e6afe64de66be1a37ff2c136b85ec","tid":1678944,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"歧視誠仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc1cef29bd13810822aeacddcb48ae6821cb4e4","tid":1678944,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"叫佢搵李澤楷問點解囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33b45dbcc01bafe3ade5f3fcd696c3e5d8ce00e","tid":1678944,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際民宣<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=34737b8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"1894f677ee7d7d1c14e31eae4a2d947aa1108ae2","tid":1678944,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"支那畜"},{"pid":"bcd53db48ef47639e6f831584dee4309751c7ae0","tid":1678944,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"